// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2024-0339 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: critical | ID: 79120fa9-2ecd-5f75-baf5-b2fcf71cc95b

any where
  (process.executable like~ "*debian:11*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:12*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:13*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:14*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:20.04-ESM*")
